{"tid":1565122,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[中秋節特輯]食蘋果日報個燈籠","createTime":"2019-09-13T04:37:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T11:03:25.000Z","uid":144435,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7fdf3e3c9dd84d4c4de52c3d6fac8c34837867c3","tid":1565122,"uid":144435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:37:56.000Z","msg":"今早正當小弟諗緊買唔買螢光棒同女女慶中秋<br />\n蘋果忽然彈咗個咁嘅post出嚟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e7XTg0v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe7XTg0v.png&h=df72736d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n哇哇哇 買報紙竟然有個咁靚嘅燈籠仔送<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小弟我都即刻入手一份<br />\n準備今晚用我呢個靚靚燈籠照爆個公園<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁啱最近成日都講環保<br />\n諗深一層 螢光棒又真係好唔環保<br />\n下次發夢又唔可以重用喎<br />\n相反呢個小燈籠 只要妥善保管<br />\n用一世都得呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n賣曬到時唔好話我有好嘢唔同大家分享<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">今晚燈籠相認，公園見！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\nP.S:個燈籠仔係印喺報紙最後個頁 要自己剪<br />\n咁多位手足唔好再咁蠢問店員個燈籠仔喺邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1472235b5dbd48f068075c70f237897489b24367","tid":1565122,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:38:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"5ce72df0b5f4a5f07281a0a0ed7f67d0156fe03f","tid":1565122,"uid":30201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:38:24.000Z","msg":"中秋自選活動 祝大家平平安安 團團圓圓<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n►人鏈活動◄<br />\n1630 石硤尾聯校人鏈&gt;集合點: 黃棣珊中學正門<br />\n1930 屯門牛牛人鏈&gt;集合點: 顯發里對出空地<br />\n2100 將軍澳人鏈&gt;調景嶺站&rarr;單車公園&larr;寶康公園<br />\n2130 沙田城門河人鏈 (直接去最接近你既河邊集合)<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n►快閃大合唱◄<br />\n1300 中環&gt;遮打花園<br />\n1300 太古&gt;OIE樓下水池<br />\n1930 屯門&gt;顯發里對出空地<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n►獅子山之路，齊慶中秋夜◄<br />\n1900 大圍、樂富、黃大仙等入口集合<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n►18區賞燈晚會 ◄ (如無注明則2030開始)<br />\n【新界西】<br />\n屯門顯發里對出空地 (承接大合唱)<br />\n屯門公園<br />\n天水圍公園<br />\n元朗公園<br />\n荃灣公園海濱長廊<br />\n葵涌運動場籃球場，林士德遊樂場<br />\n青衣海濱長廊<br />\n【新界東】<br />\n1900 上水陳融中學旁紅場<br />\n沙田中央公園<br />\n大埔海濱公園 ，大埔中央公園<br />\n馬鞍山公園<br />\n將軍澳海濱公園，寶康公園<br />\n【九龍】<br />\n美孚嶺南之風<br />\n長沙灣遊樂場<br />\n深水埗通州街遊樂場<br />\n尖沙咀梳士巴利道公園<br />\n黃大仙廣場 ，摩士公園<br />\n觀塘海濱公園<br />\n油塘道遊樂場<br />\n2100 紅磡碼頭<br />\n2150 慈雲山中央球場大合唱<br />\n【港島】<br />\n維園中央草坪<br />\n鰂魚涌至西灣河海濱長廊<br />\n柴灣公園<br />\n【東涌】<br />\n東涌海濱長廊，百慕達公園"},{"pid":"e31c8f610345789fecfde79a1f37e3ce61825d21","tid":1565122,"uid":144435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:47:38.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"86f63ab130564f310f957c5230541e7a762b6f64","tid":1565122,"uid":144435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:47:49.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"2582db26b76465d30e309836bf8530dc6750be8b","tid":1565122,"uid":144435,"like":0,"dislike":0,